ckquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲FF過講故台既故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw九成又係01想為23條造勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n似係林鄭想郁鳩中策組而放出黎<br />\n<br />\n除左林鄭同689 有邊個拎到呢d檔案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅底01自然有佢方法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭冇咁既手腕</blockquote><br />\n但除此之外真係諗唔到放出黎有咩謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇下上邊篇文既第一段 同埋呢條link<br />\n<br />\n【疑似中策組密件】預視中共發展：執政地位穩固　民主化短期難見<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/article/103894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F103894&d=s1hr%2F1EoCLrJJYSnsKJ%2Bd%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=82bf2546\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/article/103894</a><br />\n<br />\n呢份野會得罪中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放呢份野出黎會兩邊不討好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢份野都算make sense<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未必得罪中共既<br />\n始終都有話佢政權穩固</blockquote><br />\n一個小小既地方政府智囊組織 走去分析成個國家既政治制度同埋未來 中央政府會點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n輕則覺得你對中央無信心，唔係從心而發咁信服佢<br />\n重則就覺得你圖謀不軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中策組由高靜芝揸莊<br />\n條友本身已經係左王黎，分分鐘仲係黨員<br />\n做呢d分析都係為takeover香港姐<br />\n應該就唔會得罪中共<br />\n我都係有興趣邊個放料多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放料果條友想提醒某人<br />\n中策組仲有幾多左王勢力<br />\n咁岩係選舉果個人提倡改組中策組職權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利伸：ff"},{"pid":"8589bc0132303e1b2ce011cf2bff244c593afa09","tid":317055,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:22:52.